_:Nd9eedfd849064382aed80b9c1d69dc11 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Tunde Olanrewaju <abbr title=\"Commander of the Order of the British Empire\">CBE</abbr> is a Senior Partner with McKinsey and Company based in the London office, and Managing Partner for Europe, leading the firm’s practice across 23 countries. He is also a member of the firm’s global leadership team, the Enablement Team.</p>\n\n<p>He was previously the firm’s Global Chief Technology Officer and helped create McKinsey Digital, building out design, software engineering, analytics and <abbr title=\"artificial intelligence\">AI</abbr> capabilities for clients. He works across a range of sectors on strategy, operations, organisation and <abbr title=\"artificial intelligence\">AI</abbr>/Digital transformation.</p>\n\n<p>Tunde is a trustee of Oxfam <abbr title=\"Great Britain\">GB</abbr>, an independent member of Imperial College Council, and on the board of Innovate UK. He was made a Commander of the Order of the British Empire (<abbr title=\"Commander of the Order of the British Empire\">CBE</abbr>) in the King’s Birthday Honours 2025 for services to Business.</p>\n\n" .
_:N2229e35a41e74a58bf12b92496f266ee <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://schema.org/BreadcrumbList> .
